description: When Daisy gets a horrifying glimpse of the future, S.H.I.E.L.D. races to prove that fate is not fixed.
name: Spacetime
Triple Hot Dog Sandwich on Wheat

description: Kara gains a new ally when the Flash arrives from an alternate universe and helps her fight the Silver Banshee and Livewire in exchange for her helping him return home.
name: Worlds Finest

description: Steamboats on the Mississippi River are disappearing at an alarming rate. Jim West is sent to uncover the truth. The disappearances are the work of the "Thousand Eyes", a gang of pirates led by Captain Ansel Coffin, a blind man out for revenge.
name: The Night of a Thousand Eyes

description: After Gordon is removed from protective custody, he begin's to face new threat's and danger's inside prison wall's in order to survive he must rely on a new friend as well as Bullock and other outside help. Meanwhile, Penguin grow's closer to his Father, while his step-mother and step-siblings move forward with their own plan's for the family.
name: Prisoners

description:
Japanese title: Tsu hito (吊人)

A CCG prison bus is attacked by Aogiri Tree members. At Anteiku, Touka and Hinami find out that Kaneki is involved in the attack, but each react to the news in different ways, prompting Hinami to try to be less of an imposition upon Touka.
name: Hangman

description:
Japanese title: Shinsō (深層)

Amon and Akira visit Cochlea in order to get information about the Owl from Amon's former foster father, Donato Porpora. However, while they are there, the facility comes under attack by a large number of Aogiri Tree ghouls, led by Kaneki and Ayato!
name: Deeper Layers

description:
Japanese title: Kiretsu (裂目)

After living together at a CCG children's home years earlier, Kurona, Nashiro, and Suzuya are reunited in combat at Cochlea. Ayato faces an uphill battle against Shinohara, who is equipped with armor created from the remnants of his own father, Arata.
name: Rift

description: After the shocking revelation of Zoom's real identity, Barry is more determined than ever to get back to Earth-2 to stop Zoom forever. Desperate to find a way to increase his speed, Barry decides to travel back in time and masquerade as his earlier self in order to get his arch-nemesis, Dr. Harrison Wells/Eobard Thawne, to teach him how to run faster. However, things do not go as planned and Barry is stunned to face familiar foe Hartley Rathaway, as well as old friend Eddie Thawne. Iris makes peace with her past in order to embrace her future
name: Flash Back

description: Ahsoka, Kanan, and Ezra gain information about the Sith from a mysterious new ally but when Vader arrives they are quickly overwhelmed.
name: Twilight of the Apprentice

description: The Bug-Eyed Bandit escapes from jail and turns up at Palmer Tech threatening to kill everyone in the building unless she gets the bio-chip that was implanted in Felicity's spine.
name: Beacon of Hope

description: SARA RETURNS TO THE LEAGUE OF ASSASSINS – Ray (Brandon Routh), Sara (Caity Lotz) and Kendra (Ciara Renée) are shocked after they watch the Waverider fly off without them, leaving them stranded in the ‘50s. After waiting months for their teammates to come back, the three realize they must move on with their lives. Ray and Kendra bond as a couple but Sara decides to return to the League of Assassins and Ra’s al Ghul (guest star Matt Nable).
name: Left Behind

description:
Japanese title: Chiji (千路)

Suzuya's hellish boyhood is revisited, and it is revealed how he came to work for CCG. As Touka studies for her entrance exams, Roma, a new waitress, fills in for her at Anteiku. Tempers erupt when Akira joins Amon and Seido for supper.
name: Thousand Paths

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: Proper Japanese Title: サイヤ人の誇りを忘れるな！ベジータＶＳ第６宇宙のサイヤ人 (Saiya-jin no Hokori o Wasureru na! Bejīta Tai Dai-Roku Uchū no Saiya-jin)
name: Don't Forget Your Saiyan Pride! Vegeta vs the Saiyan of Universe 6

description: S.H.I.E.L.D. hunts for information on their dangerous new enemy, and a shameful secret from Malick’s past is exposed, threatening to destroy his HYDRA legacy.
name: Paradise Lost

description:
Japanese title: Tōka (透過)

Tsukiyama shows up at Anteiku with news for Yoshimura about Kaneki's attempt to become a kakuja via serial ghoul cannibalism. Concerned over her "Big Brother," Hinami accompanies Tsukiyama to a coffee shop, where she again runs into Takatsuki.
name: Permeation

description:
Japanese title: Kyū kyū (旧九)

During Kaneki's visit with Yoshimura, he asks for information about the Owl, and is told the tragic tale of a young ghoul named Kuzen. Touka makes plans to move out of Anteiku. A snowy day brings with it brisk business at the coffee shop.
name: Old Nines

description:
Japanese title: Machi mochi (街望)

Yoshitoki is granted permission to execute the operation to eradicate the Owl. The many CCG officers involved in the mission take time beforehand to write any last words they might have, as the 20th Ward is cordoned off and its civilians evacuated.
name: City in Waiting

description:
Japanese title: Tsui ame (終雨)

The battle between CCG and Anteiku continues, and Koma, Irimi, and Yoshimura each engage the special investigators. When a civilian gets caught in the middle, Hachikawa continues to press his attack unabated. Shinohara receives some unexpected advice.
name: Last Rain

description:
Japanese title: Mitsuru hana (溢花)

Suzuya is left to face the newly-arrived one-eyed Owl on his own. Aogiri Tree joins the battle against CCG, who find themselves overwhelmed by the sheer number of opponents. Meanwhile, Kaneki confronts Amon, who stands in his way to Anteiku.
name: Deluge of Flowers

description: Alexandria is alerted after realizing someone is missing. Several search parties will venture out, but what they find isn't what they're hoping for.
name: East

description: To save one of their own, Rick's group must venture outside the walls. Their experience there will change their lives forever.
name: Last Day on Earth

description:
Japanese title: Ken (研)

Kaneki and Hide are reunited, and the two of them revisit the times they spent together. Kaneki and Touka separately remember the other members of Anteiku, as both they and CCG cope with their losses.
name: Ken

deck: For ignoring a warning to stay away from Melkotian territory, members of The Enterprise crew are sentenced to die in a reenactment of the Gunfight at the O.K. Corral.
description: The Enterprise encounters a buoy in space that sends a message warning them to avoid trespassing in Melkotian space. Undaunted Kirk leads an away team down to the surface of the planet Theta Kiokis II in an attempt to communicate with the Melkotians. The team, which consists of Kirk, Spock, Mr. Scott, Dr. McCoy and Ensign Chekov is confronted by a being that tells them since they ignored the warning they are to die by a punishment chosen from Kirk's mind, since he gave the order to trespass. Instantly the team finds themselves in what appears to be Tombstone, Arizona on October 26th, 1881.
name: Spectre of the Gun

description: Oliver and Diggle find out Merlyn wants to break Darhk out of prison; Laurel gets a surprise offer.
name: Eleven-Fifty-Nine

description: Rip (Arthur Darvill) tells the team they are headed to the future to take out a powerful ally that Savage (guest star Casper Crump) needs in order to conquer the world. However, when Rip reveals the ally is a 14 year-old boy (guest star Cory Gruter-Andrew) who will one day grow into an evil dictator, the team is split about the morality of killing a child, even if it does save the world. Meanwhile, Sara (Caity Lotz) talks Snart (Wentworth Miller) through a rough patch and Ray (Brandon Routh) learns something that could impact his future with Kendra (Ciara Renée).
name: Progeny

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: Proper Japanese Title: 第６宇宙最強の戦士！殺し屋ヒット見参！(Dai-Roku Uchū Saikyō no Senshi! Koroshiya Hitto Kenzan!!)
name: The Supreme Warrior of the Universe #6! An assassin named Hit!!

description: Agent Daisy Johnson must call upon the Secret Warriors for an inaugural mission that will leave no member unscathed, and S.H.I.E.L.D. learns more about Hive's powers, forcing them to question everyone they trust.
name: The Team

deck: Non and Indigo use mind control to make the citizens of National City their army
description: Non and Indigo use mind control to make the citizens of National City their army, so Kara must find a way to save her friends.
name: Myriad

deck: In an attempt to clear his name, Gordon steals his case file and approaches Nygma for help
description: In an attempt to clear his name, Gordon steals his case file and approaches Nygma for help. Meanwhile, Penguin discovers his step-family's role in his father's death, and awakens from his conditioning.
name: Into the Woods

description: Bubbles wins two tickets to a concert and has to pick between Blossom and Buttercup to go with her. Meanwhile, the Mayor's plane goes down over Monster Island and it's up to the girls to rescue him.
name: Escape from Monster Island

description: Buttercup becomes enamored with a team of roller derby girls called the Derbytantes. When she starts spending all of her time with them, Princess Morbucks seeks to be her replacement in the Powerpuff Girls.
name: Princess Buttercup

description: Blossom and Buttercup suffer a candy hangover, and they must retrace their steps to find where they left Bubbles.
name: The Stayover

description: A rainbow causes Townsville to become uncomfortably happy.
name: Painbow

description: Donny the Pony is transformed into a monster that threatens Townsville.
name: Horn Sweet Horn

description: Buttercup adopts a New Age attitude after letting Man-Boy the villain escape in her anger. In order to defeat Man-Boy when he returns to take revenge, Buttercup aims to strike a balance between inner peace and struggle.
name: Man Up

description: The Mayor of Townsville overworks the Powerpuff Girls after his secretary Sara Bellum goes on vacation.
name: Bye Bye Bellum
